  "notes": [
    "Schedule D (Form 1040) AcroForm widget map for the IRS-hosted TY2025 PDF (PDF /Title metadata: '2025 Schedule D (Form 1040)').",
    "Part I (short-term) has four rows: 1a (aggregate totals w/ basis reported, not listed on 8949), 1b (detail-listed totals, basis reported), 2 (basis NOT reported), 3 (not on 1099-B). Each row has four money columns: (d) proceeds, (e) cost basis, (g) adjustment amount, (h) gain/loss.",
    "Part II (long-term) mirrors Part I with rows 8a/8b/9/10 and the same four columns.",
    "Line 16 (total gain/loss) and the Part III worksheet lines 17-22 live on page 2. Line 17/20/22 are Yes/No checkbox pairs; only the Yes box is mapped and the No box is in unmapped_widgets.",
    "The digital-asset Yes/No pair (c1_1[0]/[1]) on page 1 is NOT yet wired to Layer 1 - wave 7 will route the canonical return's digital_asset_disposition flag here.",
    "Form 8949 transaction detail is rendered in a separate map (form-8949-acroform-map.json); Schedule D line 1b/2/3/8b/9/10 totals are summed from the 8949 Layer 1 totals."
  ],
